    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bottles, usually glass and cylindrical, with sloping shoulders and a medium-length neck. They are designed to be plugged or capped, and intended to contain carbonated beverages.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
